34:33.505 --> 34:36.208
* I loved you from the moment
that I saw you *

34:36.242 --> 34:39.478
* You're my hero,
I believe in you *

34:39.511 --> 34:41.746
* There's nothing you can't do

34:41.780 --> 34:45.217
* You make a difference
in the world *

34:45.251 --> 34:49.487
* And you make all the
difference in the world *

34:49.521 --> 34:52.791
* To... me....

34:54.926 --> 34:57.896
Oh, my God, Josh,
I... (laughs)

34:57.929 --> 35:00.299
I told you,
when I was that age,

35:00.332 --> 35:03.302
I was really dramatic and weird,
and I was so hormonal,

35:03.335 --> 35:04.570
so whatever I said
in this letter...

35:04.603 --> 35:06.705
Rebecca, what you said

35:06.738 --> 35:09.441
about believing in me, about...

35:09.475 --> 35:12.378
truly understanding who I am,

35:12.411 --> 35:16.148
no one has ever said
anything like that about me.

35:20.919 --> 35:23.622
Do you mind if I keep it?

35:23.655 --> 35:26.358
Not at all. Please.

35:26.392 --> 35:28.927
Cool.

35:28.960 --> 35:32.398
You know, all my life, I've
wondered if I was good enough

35:32.431 --> 35:36.402
or smart enough,

35:36.435 --> 35:39.938
but now I know
you've always believed in me.

35:39.971 --> 35:42.808
You always support me
in who I am.

35:42.841 --> 35:45.277
Getting me hired at Aloha's

35:45.311 --> 35:47.579
and coming to this camp.

35:47.613 --> 35:49.915
I love this camp.

35:54.220 --> 35:58.257
You never tried to change me.

35:58.290 --> 36:00.259
That means so much.

36:00.292 --> 36:01.827
You have no idea.

36:05.997 --> 36:07.699
It's ironic.

36:07.733 --> 36:09.435
You came here
to empower some girls,

36:09.468 --> 36:12.838
but instead you empowered
this goofball.

36:12.871 --> 36:15.607
(both chuckle)

36:37.629 --> 36:39.365
See you later, Becks.

36:43.335 --> 36:45.304
Bye.

36:45.337 --> 36:46.838
What the hell?

36:46.872 --> 36:48.907
You're a grown-ass woman.

36:48.940 --> 36:50.476
He should have been
kissing you on your mouth.

36:50.509 --> 36:52.478
Yeah, she's still
thirsty, Josh.

36:52.511 --> 36:55.647
Uh-uh,
I'm not thirsty anymore, Tanya.

36:57.283 --> 36:59.485
Right now,

36:59.518 --> 37:01.520
in this moment...

37:01.553 --> 37:03.889
(sighs)
I feel quenched.

37:03.922 --> 37:05.957
Gross.

37:10.462 --> 37:13.699
I'm, uh, I'm not ready
to say good-bye to this pâté.

37:13.732 --> 37:15.867
You mind if I take some with me?
Absolutely.

37:15.901 --> 37:17.002
Hey, you know what,

37:17.035 --> 37:18.770
you don't have to stick around
and help me clean up.

37:18.804 --> 37:20.672
Honestly, I mean, everybody
else has already bailed.

37:20.706 --> 37:22.408
Oh, no, no, it's cool, bro.

37:22.441 --> 37:24.676
I was also the social director
of my fraternity,

37:24.710 --> 37:27.546
so I also know that everyone
leaves you with a wet bathroom.

37:27.579 --> 37:29.381
How does it get so wet?

37:29.415 --> 37:31.550
No one knows.
(laughs)

37:31.583 --> 37:34.653
Hey, you know why I really
wanted to have a party?

37:34.686 --> 37:35.687
Huh?

37:35.721 --> 37:37.423
Well, it's just...

37:37.456 --> 37:39.691
like, it's really tough on me
when my daughter isn't around.

37:39.725 --> 37:40.959
I get a little sad.

37:40.992 --> 37:44.563
Just wanted to be
a little less... lonely,

37:44.596 --> 37:45.831
make some friends.

37:45.864 --> 37:48.967
Well, you made one.

37:49.000 --> 37:50.702
That girl with the tube top?

37:50.736 --> 37:52.438
No, I... I paid for her.

37:52.471 --> 37:54.506
I paid for all the
girls, actually.

37:54.540 --> 37:55.741
Uh...

37:55.774 --> 37:58.344
Oh, I'm sorry, you mean you.

37:58.377 --> 38:00.879
Yeah, yeah, that's...
(chuckles) that's what I meant.

38:00.912 --> 38:02.614
Oh, thank you.

38:02.648 --> 38:03.915
All right, I better jet.

38:06.117 --> 38:07.353
All right.
There you go.

38:07.386 --> 38:09.020
Yeah. Yeah.

38:13.392 --> 38:15.361
Later, bro.

38:15.394 --> 38:17.396
*

38:21.467 --> 38:23.001
Oof.

38:27.639 --> 38:29.608
*

38:37.816 --> 38:39.785
My health insurance
doesn't cover therapy,

38:39.818 --> 38:41.520
so I'm stuck with this.

38:41.553 --> 38:44.523
But it was in the library's free
book bin, so you know it's good.

38:44.556 --> 38:46.792
There is a dead spider
sticking out of the binding.

38:46.825 --> 38:49.060
So far it's been really fun.

38:49.094 --> 38:50.929
I've learned a lot

38:50.962 --> 38:54.800
about being emotionally naked.

38:54.833 --> 38:58.904
Ew. Throw on
an emotional robe, please.

38:58.937 --> 39:02.040
Heather, seriously, I'm sorry.

39:02.073 --> 39:05.043
If someone even hints
about being exclusive,

39:05.076 --> 39:07.045
I get nervous that
they're gonna bail.

39:07.078 --> 39:10.616
And according to this book,
it's because I am a...

39:10.649 --> 39:12.684
"dumbass."

39:12.718 --> 39:13.952
That's cool.

39:13.985 --> 39:15.687
You are who you are.

39:15.721 --> 39:17.956
So... bye.

39:17.989 --> 39:19.625
Uh, where are you going?

39:19.658 --> 39:21.493
I get real for one minute,
and you're out?

39:21.527 --> 39:24.362
Sorry, it's just
that I have a date.

39:26.732 --> 39:28.434
Is it Zeke?

39:28.467 --> 39:29.701
I drunk-Googled him.

39:30.602 --> 39:31.570
I get it.

39:31.603 --> 39:33.439
The abs, the tats, it works.

39:33.472 --> 39:34.440
No.

39:34.473 --> 39:36.975
Uh, the movie starts at 7:00.

39:37.008 --> 39:39.445
The date is with you, dummy.

39:39.478 --> 39:41.513
I was, like,
trying to do a cute thing.

39:41.547 --> 39:44.783
Again, s...
(laughs) so subtle.

39:44.816 --> 39:46.785
I... I'm in.

39:46.818 --> 39:49.621
I commit to this movie.

39:49.655 --> 39:51.156
Okay.

39:51.189 --> 39:54.460
But if we do this again,
you can't be an idiot this time.

39:54.493 --> 39:56.462
Never again.

39:56.495 --> 39:57.596
Come on, let's go.

39:57.629 --> 39:59.598
No, no, no, no, no, no.

40:02.934 --> 40:04.470
You need this.

40:04.503 --> 40:06.037
Yes, I do.

40:07.506 --> 40:08.874
(sighs)

40:14.980 --> 40:16.782
(door opens)

40:16.815 --> 40:18.517
How was your last trip to camp?

40:18.550 --> 40:20.051
Was it sad to say good-bye?

40:20.085 --> 40:21.553
I don't know...

40:24.723 --> 40:26.224
...'cause I didn't.

40:26.257 --> 40:27.493
Excuse me?

40:27.526 --> 40:29.495
I'm going back every year.

40:29.528 --> 40:30.496
It's who I am.

40:30.529 --> 40:32.498
It's important to me.

40:32.531 --> 40:34.533
I can't believe
you're talking to me like this.

40:34.566 --> 40:36.535
It's called empowerment.

40:41.206 --> 40:43.174
(humming)

40:43.208 --> 40:47.178
You know, they say you
can't go back in time.

40:47.212 --> 40:49.180
But "they" are dumb.

40:49.214 --> 40:51.517
'Cause you totally can.

40:51.550 --> 40:53.519
That trip to camp was a triumph.

40:53.552 --> 40:56.788
I mean, it wasn't just
a victory, it was a mandate.

40:56.822 --> 40:58.056
Like, you could invade

40:58.089 --> 41:00.058
any country
that you wanted to right now,

41:00.091 --> 41:01.693
because...

41:01.727 --> 41:03.529
he kissed you.

41:03.562 --> 41:06.097
I mean, he didn't kiss me,
he just kissed me on the cheek.

41:06.131 --> 41:07.833
Um, it's the way
that he kissed you.

41:07.866 --> 41:11.202
And listen to me,
a kiss on the cheek means...

41:11.236 --> 41:12.704
What does it mean?

41:13.705 --> 41:14.673
What does it mean?

41:14.706 --> 41:15.707
What-what does it mean?

41:17.776 --> 41:21.046
Well, sometimes
it means nothing.

41:21.079 --> 41:22.548
Mmm.

41:22.581 --> 41:23.815
Uh, sometimes it means
it's your Aunt Lucy,

41:23.849 --> 41:25.283
and she hasn't seen you
since you were 11,

41:25.316 --> 41:26.952
but sometimes...

41:26.985 --> 41:29.855
sometimes it means...

41:31.823 --> 41:34.793
...everything.

41:34.826 --> 41:36.828
It does?
It does?

41:40.065 --> 41:41.066
(both sigh)

41:46.071 --> 41:47.773
(banging)
MAN: Come on, Chloe.

41:47.806 --> 41:49.307
Let me out of the box.

41:49.340 --> 41:50.375
Say it again.

41:50.408 --> 41:53.311
MAN: Female wage disparity
needs to be rectified

41:53.344 --> 41:55.113
through congressional action.

41:55.146 --> 41:56.615
Good boy.

41:58.016 --> 42:01.186
MAN: Ugh, that was worth
at least three almonds.

